 though the reach was just 4.25 inches. At 16 inches, it had a 750-lux brightness, which is far below the recommended level. This means you have to sit very close to the lamp, even to get just 5,000 lux. Even at a foot away, the light&#39;s brightness was less than 2,000 lux. By comparison though, the Full-Size HappyLight was much worse. It had a 10,000-lux reach of just 2.5 inches and measured just 200 lux at 16 inches.","The HappyLight has a color temperature of 6,500 Kelvin. That’s 1,500 Kelvin over the recommended range set by the Center for Environmental Therapeutics (CET), an organization of experts on light therapy. Despite being free of UV radiation, the CET doesn’t recommend cooler, bluish lights over 5,000 Kelvin because they can cause aversive glare and potentially damage your retinas if you take photosensitizing medications. The full-spectrum fluorescent light bulbs don&#39;t seem particularly blue until you see them turned on next to other light therapy lamps.","This Verilux HappyLight had an interesting heat output. The lamp’s surface reached 135 degrees Fahrenheit. And while it’s certainly not the hottest lamp, it was hotter than most lights I tested. However, when I aimed it at a wall from 16 inches away, it only increased the wall’s surface temperature by 0.25 degrees. That isn’t significant enough to feel. So, while the lamp itself gets pretty warm, the heat dissipates quickly and shouldn&#39;t make you uncomfortably hot during therapy sessions.","<strong>Summary</strong>","The HappyLight Compact performed surprisingly well for its size. In fact, it was brighter than even its Full-Size counterpart. However, its light lacks the reach to provide the necessary brightness at a comfortable distance, so you have to extend your therapy sessions."]},"id":"0b7a88a7-f4c8-48c8-82eb-334380b93993","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_70328","url":"/verilux-happylight-compact-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeph-preece","url":"/author/jeph-preece","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Jeph Preece","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"UEqrRM5xmXnCHCjkbS6o5e","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2018-10-31T18:13:37Z","datePublished":"2018-10-31T18:13:37Z","name":"Verilux HappyLight Compact","synopsis":"Verilux makes several versions of the HappyLight light therapy box. I tested the Full-Size and Compact versions. In a surprising twist, the Compact was the better performing lamp, despite being much smaller.","review":{"rating":67,"verdict":"The Verilux HappyLight Compact isn&#8217;t built to be the brightest light therapy lamp &#8211; rather, it&#8217;s designed to be portable. Still, it performed better than Verilux&#8217;s full-size version.","pros":["It performs well for its size."],"cons":["The lamp&#8217;s brightness reach is subpar."]},"strapline":"Verilux makes several versions of the HappyLight light therapy box. I tested the Full-Size and Compact versions. In a surprising twist, the Compact was the better performing lamp, despite being much smaller.","language":"en","dateModified":"2018-11-09T00:00:00Z","id":"4tyK6Deavi23rFy4AyEDx5","meta":{"title":"Verilux HappyLight Compact Review | Top Ten Reviews","description":"Visit Top Ten Reviews to read the latest reviews and opinions. Reviews are complete with product ratings and comparisons."},"products":[{"slug":"verilux-happylight-compact","url":"/product/verilux-happylight-compact","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T20:19:15Z","name":"Verilux HappyLight Compact","dateModified":"2019-04-16T20:19:15Z","id":"mvUvkRaiuxuf5PPnNBBrAP","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-16T20:19:15Z","type":"review","template":"review","social":{"twitter":{"image":{"status":"","height":0,"path":"/oR4QdsW9qXEwQgSt9ym9nZ.jpg","checksum":"","copyright":"","fileSize":0,"width":0,"caption":"","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T20:19:15Z","mimeType":"","name"